<h2>Shipping Policy</h2>

<p>
    Following are the terms and conditions that constitute our Shipping Policy.
    <br />
    <br />
    All order over $100 will be shipped free of charge.
    <br />
    <br />
    All orders are processed within 2-3 business days. Orders are not shipped or delivered on
    weekends or holidays.
    <br />
    If we are experiencing a high volume of orders, shipments may be delayed by a few days. Please
    allow additional days in transit for delivery.
    <br />
    If there will be a significant delay in shipment of your order, we will contact you.
    <br />
    <br />
    * Overnight delivery is only available for orders with delivery addresses within Israel.
    <br />
    Delivery delays can occasionally occur.

</p>
